Roles &amp; Responsibility 主要职责

？Be Responsible for employee pre-on boarding process including but not limit to candidate communication, internal process tracking, new hire survey and exit survey;
Implement the staff engagement process and procedure (from entry to exit) to ensure the staff engagement is conducted in effective and consistent way and responsible for implementation.
Support the staffing activities and projects, including but not limit to on-board, exit, contract renew, probation, promotion, internal transfer and etc. under related HR policies and procedures;
Employee Relationship Support: 1. ER case support 2. Work injury application 3. Retirement application with vendor support 4. Employee emergency case support 5. Expat work permit support;
Continuous improvement in HR Operation process to lead operation process optimization;
SF EC module master user;
Be responsible for HRIS data accuracy and completeness;
Participate in various HR projects and execute assigned project activities;
P-file and HR Operation document management: manage all p-files in the filing room (5 sites), ensure all p-files updated in time;
Support on recruitment channels and make the channel efficiency analysis and reporting.
Support on both online and offline recruitment solutions in employer branding and engagement.
Support various HR initiatives and projects.
Manage recruitment database, ensure that it is up-to-date and generate reports on a regular basis for the team and business.
Others tasks assigned;


Job Requirement 工作要求

？Bachelor degree
At least 5 years working experience in Human Resources
English as working language
Agility and resilience. Can be open minded to changes and improvement opportunities.
Independent and with a strong sense of responsibility
Learning ability. Fast learner and always willing to learn.
Result driven, detail Oriented Familiar with HR systems, experience with SucessFactor is a plus
